OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FLily Allen has spoken of a "really
OL,7,Ftough few days" involving receiving
OL,8,Fdeath threats online, after it emerged
OL,9,Fshe returned her puppy to a dog
OL,10,Fshelter in 2021.
OL,12,FOn Saturday, animal rights charity
OL,13,FPETA published an open letter to the
OL,14,FBritish singer, after she shared a
OL,15,Fstory on her podcast about getting rid
OL,16,Fof a dog she adopted in the pandemic
OL,17,Fwhich chewed her family's passports.
