OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FPETA said in a post on X: "Lily,
OL,7,Fplease don't treat dogs as accessories
OL,8,Fto be discarded when they become
OL,9,Finconvenient. It's not fair and it's
OL,10,Freally not ok.
OL,12,F"We're sending Lily a mechanical toy
OL,13,Fdog, which requires none of the round-
OL,14,Fthe-clock care a real-life puppy does."
