OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FIn response to the criticism, Allen
OL,7,Fsaid on Sunday: "People have been
OL,8,Ffuriously reacting to a deliberately
OL,9,Fdistorted cobbling together of quotes
OL,10,Fdesigned to make people angry and as a
OL,11,Fresult, I've received some really
OL,12,Fabhorrent messages including death
OL,13,Fthreats."
OL,15,FShe described how puppy Mary developed
OL,16,Fsevere separation anxiety and could
OL,17,Fnot be left alone, which led the
OL,18,Ffamily to work with a behavioral
OL,19,Fspecialist and professional trainer.
