OL,11,FThe rehoming happened with someone who
OL,12,Fwas known to Allen, she explained, a
OL,13,Fprocess which happened within 24 hours
OL,14,Fof her being returned to the shelter.
OL,16,F"We couldn't meet Mary's needs and her
OL,17,Fhappiness and welfare were central to
OL,18,Fus making that decision, as difficult
OL,19,Fas it was," she said.
