OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FAllen lives in New York with her
OL,7,Fhusband David Harbour, an actor and
OL,8,Fstar of hit Netflix show Stranger
OL,9,FThings.
OL,11,FIn an episode of her podcast Miss Me?,
OL,12,FAllen told listeners how they were
OL,13,Fconsidering adopting another puppy but
OL,14,Fwere hesitant to do so because of
OL,15,Ftheir prior experiences.
OL,17,FThe singer has two children with ex-
OL,18,Fhusband Sam Cooper, who is based in
OL,19,Fthe UK.
