OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FShe said: "(The dog) ate all three of
OL,7,Four passports and they had our visas
OL,8,Fin and I cannot tell you how much
OL,9,Fmoney it cost me to get everything
OL,10,Freplaced because it was in COVID. And
OL,11,Fso it was just an absolutely
OL,12,Flogistical nightmare.
OL,14,F"And because the father of my children
OL,15,Flives in England, I couldn't get them
OL,16,Fback to see their dad for like four
OL,17,Fmonths, five months, because this
OL,18,Ff****ing dog had eaten their passports.
OL,20,F"I just couldn't look at her. I was
OL,21,Flike, 'You've ruined my life'."
