OL,3,CLily Allen faced 'death threats' after
OL,4,Crevealing she returned dog to shelter
OL,6,FAllen said the response to her
OL,7,Fanecdote was "very distressing", and
OL,8,Fsaid she had never before been accused
OL,9,Fof mistreating animals.
OL,11,FShe urged people to avoid "clickbait
OL,12,Farticles" and to exercise due
OL,13,Fdiligence when reading content about
OL,14,Fher online.
OL,16,FResponding directly to PETA, the star
OL,17,Fposted on X: "Also thank you to PETA
OL,18,Ffor adding fuel to the fire. Very
OL,19,Fresponsible of you."
